      • replace

        T replace(int givenPosition,
          T newEntry)
        Replace an item at a particular position by the given newEntry.
        Parameters:
        givenPosition - The position whose item is to be replaced.
        newEntry - The object of the newEntry to be replaced.
        Returns:
        The original item previous the the givenPosition. Pre-condition: isEmpty() is called and made sure that it returns false otherwise a SecurityException is thrown. The number of entries >= givenPosition. newEntry is not null. Post-condition: the number of entrie is the same.
